lead_paragraph: The stopwatch never lies they say in Formula One but in Nico Rosberg's case it did and that was one of several things which went wrong for the German in a woeful home race on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Faulty Stopwatch Adds to Rosberg’s Germany Woes
